      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_003",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我只能无奈地在车里等待，心里非常着急",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "char_start": 69,
      "char_end": 89,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "好不容易回到家，我开始喝酒",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "char_start": 90,
      "char_end": 103,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "不久，老友也来了，他告诉我他失恋了，心里很难过",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "char_start": 104,
      "char_end": 129,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我笑着安慰他，劝他不要再想那些不开心的事",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "char_start": 130,
      "char_end": 152,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们一起喝酒，时间慢慢流逝",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "char_start": 153,
      "char_end": 166,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "后来，老友要坐公交车回家，外面下起了雨",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "char_start": 167,
      "char_end": 188,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我在楼下等他，他问我是不是和那个女人分手了，是不是坐公交车",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "char_start": 189,
      "char_end": 221,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我告诉他是的，并且指向了天上的乌云",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "char_start": 222,
      "char_end": 241,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "他说下雨了，没有太阳，还问我要不要伞",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "char_start": 242,
      "char_end": 263,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我同意了",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "char_start": 264,
      "char_end": 269,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们在雨中等待公交车，他去了趟卫生间",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "char_start": 270,
      "char_end": 291,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "等了很久，他终于出来了，还亲了我一下",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "char_start": 292,
      "char_end": 313,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们继续喝酒，我感到非常开心",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "char_start": 314,
      "char_end": 330,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "最后，他回家了，我一个人站在雨中，心里有些难过，不知道他什么时候才能走出失恋的阴影",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 331,
      "char_end": 378,
      "children": []
    }
